article_title: Under Obamacare, Does Everyone Drive A Cadillac?

article_metadata.description: It is looking more and more as if the Cadillac tax is not a tax on very rich and excess health plans but on everyman plans, and cuts are coming to many.
article_metadata.author: Robert W. Wood
